{
  "total_duration": 856.194,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 6.62,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象一个小村庄。村里有个大家都认识的人，叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam Benton"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 6.97,
      "end": 18.642,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是本地"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "butcher"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是卖肉的店主。这样的人在小村庄里不是陌生人，大家买东西会见到他，路上也会打招呼。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 18.991,
      "end": 36.971,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有一天，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "带着自己攒下来的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "savings"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "去"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "savings"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是存款，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在老式社区里也可能处理一些钱款服务。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 37.32,
      "end": 42.12,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结果，钱包丢了。不是几枚硬币，而是一大笔钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 42.47,
      "end": 48.158,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "村子很小，消息很快传开："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的钱不见了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 48.508,
      "end": 58.656,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "心里也明白，这钱包大概不是掉进河里了，而是被村里某个人捡到了。可是，没有人来还。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 59.006,
      "end": 67.294,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "三个月后，一个早晨，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "打开门，发现门口放着一个用报纸包起来的钱包。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 67.644,
      "end": 80.003,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "钱包回来了，但里面只有一半的钱，还有一张纸条。那个人好像在跟自己的良心谈判：我是小偷，是的，但我只是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "50 per cent a thief"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 80.353,
      "end": 85.441,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是今天的题目："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A clear conscience"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，问心无愧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 85.791,
      "end": 96.167,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Conscience"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以理解成心里的良心声音。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A clear conscience"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是心里没有亏欠，晚上能睡得踏实。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 96.517,
      "end": 104.237,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是这篇课文的笑点就在这里：钱可以分期还，诚实真的能分期变回来吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 104.587,
      "end": 136.062,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天背诵不要先硬背一长串英文。先记中文电影线：全村知道丢钱 ->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "丢钱包 -> 带"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "savings"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "去"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "-> 觉得有人捡了但没还 -> 三个月后钱包回来一半 ->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "50%"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小偷 -> 又还一些 ->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "25%"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小偷 -> 最后全还清 ->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "100% honest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 136.412,
      "end": 138.732,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一段，丢钱传开。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 139.081,
      "end": 144.789,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：全村都知道，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "丢了一大笔钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 145.139,
      "end": 153.575,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对应的英文块是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The whole village soon learnt"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a large sum of money had been lost"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 153.925,
      "end": 165.396,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A large sum of money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一大笔钱。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Had been lost"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是过去完成被动，重点放在钱已经丢了这个结果上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 165.746,
      "end": 171.41,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后人物出现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam Benton, the local butcher, had lost his wallet"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 171.76,
      "end": 181.616,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Local butcher"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是本地卖肉的店主。这个背景很重要，因为小村庄里大家认识他，所以消息会传得很快。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 181.966,
      "end": 184.286,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二段，钱包没有回来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 184.636,
      "end": 197.019,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "带着"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "savings"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "去"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，觉得钱包肯定被村民捡到了，可是没人还。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 197.369,
      "end": 205.533,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先挂住两个英文块："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "while taking his savings to the post office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been found"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 205.883,
      "end": 216.571,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Must have been found"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "没看见是谁捡的，但他很肯定，钱包一定已经被人捡到了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 216.92,
      "end": 224.992,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "形式是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "加过去分词，表示对过去被动事件的高把握推测。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 225.342,
      "end": 231.558,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面还有一句很关键："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "it was not returned to him"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。钱包没有被还给他。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 231.908,
      "end": 239.004,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是本课的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mystery grammar"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "：我们知道发生了什么，却不知道是谁做的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 239.354,
      "end": 242.834,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三段，第一次良心分期。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 243.183,
      "end": 253.591,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：三个月后，钱包出现在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "家门口，被报纸包着，里面只有一半的钱和一张纸条。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 253.941,
      "end": 265.621,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对应英文块是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Three months passed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "outside his front door"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wrapped up in newspaper"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "contained half the money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 265.971,
      "end": 273.522,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Wrapped up in newspaper"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是用报纸包起来。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Contained half the money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是里面有一半的钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 273.872,
      "end": 280.44,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接下来纸条出现了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A thief, yes, but only 50 per cent a thief!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 280.79,
      "end": 291.962,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话的中文意思不是说偷东西可以原谅，而是在制造一个荒唐笑点：他还了一半钱，就说自己只是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "50%"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小偷。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 292.312,
      "end": 299.7,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "returning half is not enough"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。还一半不是诚实，只是开始补错。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 300.05,
      "end": 302.09,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四段，逐步还清。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 302.439,
      "end": 314.959,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：又过两个月，又有一些钱送来；最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的钱全还清了，那个人说自己"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "100% honest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 315.309,
      "end": 321.581,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先记"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Two months later"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，再记"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "some more money was sent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 321.931,
      "end": 327.747,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Was sent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还是被动语态，因为送来钱的人继续匿名。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 328.096,
      "end": 333.032,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二张纸条说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Only 25 per cent a thief now!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 333.382,
      "end": 341.626,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "all Sam's money was paid back"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am 100 per cent honest now!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 341.976,
      "end": 349.272,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个结尾很"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "New Concept"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "：有点干，有点好笑，也有点刺人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 349.622,
      "end": 355.082,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他想把良心像欠款一样分期还清，可是真正的诚实不是百分比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 355.431,
      "end": 359.714,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老师，最后他把钱都还了，那是不是就问心无愧了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 360.064,
      "end": 367.104,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他确实做了一件该做的事：把钱还回去。但一开始拿走别人的钱，还是错的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 367.453,
      "end": 371.144,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以课文不是在说“偷了以后慢慢还也行”？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 371.493,
      "end": 379.333,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，完全不是。笑点是那个人给自己的良心算百分比，好像还一半就只剩一半的小偷。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 379.683,
      "end": 383.216,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Honesty"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是考试分数。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 383.565,
      "end": 397.917,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Exactly. Honesty is not a percentage score"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。诚实不是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "50%"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "25%"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "100%"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这样算出来的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 398.267,
      "end": 402.504,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "clear conscience"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到底是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 402.854,
      "end": 410.214,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是你知道自己没有亏欠，或者已经认真把错事补好了，所以心里干净、踏实。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 410.564,
      "end": 413.389,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇为什么这么多被动语态？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 413.739,
      "end": 431.086,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为做事的人一直躲在故事背后。钱"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had been lost"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，钱包"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been found"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，钱"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was sent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was paid back"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。我们看见结果，却看不见那个人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 431.436,
      "end": 434.409,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果现实里我捡到钱包呢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 434.759,
      "end": 447.103,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "立刻完整归还。交给老师、前台、保安、警察或者"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "lost-and-found office"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。不要只还一部分，更不要给自己算诚实百分比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 447.453,
      "end": 451.653,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The whole village soon learnt that a large sum of money had been lost."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 452.003,
      "end": 457.907,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam Benton, the local butcher, had lost his wallet while taking his savings to the post office."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 458.257,
      "end": 464.281,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sam was sure that the wallet must have been found by one of the villagers, but it was not returned to him."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 464.631,
      "end": 469.911,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Three months passed, and then one morning, Sam found his wallet outside his front door."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 470.261,
      "end": 479.477,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It had been wrapped up in newspaper and it contained half the money he had lost, together with a note which said: 'A thief, yes, but only 50 per cent a thief!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 479.826,
      "end": 486.33,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Two months later, some more money was sent to Sam with another note: 'Only 25 per cent a thief now!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 486.68,
      "end": 490.52,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In time, all Sam's money was paid back in this way."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 490.87,
      "end": 495.022,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The last note said: 'I am 100 per cent honest now!'"
        }
      ]
    },
