          "text": "All Sam's money was paid back"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，所有钱被还清。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 85,
      "start": 645.5,
      "end": 651.3,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么这些句子都适合被动语态？因为我们知道发生了什么，但不知道是谁做的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 86,
      "start": 651.649,
      "end": 663.373,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文把重点放在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wallet"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "note"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "result"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "上，而不是放在匿名人的脸上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 87,
      "start": 663.723,
      "end": 672.37,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再看"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been found"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pattern"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "加过去分词。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 88,
      "start": 672.72,
      "end": 680.0,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它表达的是：我没有亲眼看见，但我非常确定过去发生了这件事，而且它是被动发生的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 89,
      "start": 680.35,
      "end": 685.994,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The door is open. It must have been opened by someone."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 90,
      "start": 686.344,
      "end": 691.616,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再比如："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The cake is gone. It must have been eaten."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 91,
      "start": 691.966,
      "end": 701.765,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后看百分比笑点："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "50 per cent a thief"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "25 per cent a thief"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "100 per cent honest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 92,
      "start": 702.115,
      "end": 713.795,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "British English"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "per cent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "常常分成两个词；现代日常也会看到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "percent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "或百分号。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 93,
      "start": 714.145,
      "end": 723.993,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是在这个故事里，百分比不是数学重点，而是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "moral joke"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。钱可以分期还，诚实不能分期算。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 94,
      "start": 724.342,
      "end": 734.798,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
